February Enrichment Week 4: It's time for the Grand Finale 🏆 💖

This week, each dog will engage with a potential playmate before finally meeting snout-to-snout! Each pup is then invited to strut their stuff down our red carpet and fight for the chance to be the 'Love Unleashed' Ultimate Canine Couple! 🐾🐕

Here's what activities are on the menu:
🐾 Build Your Love Potion –
Feel the magic with a love potion mixer.
🐾 Rose Petal Pit –
Dig through the roses to find the treat.
🐾 Secret Admirer Gift –
Solve a puzzle from your potential match.
🐾 Paw Painting Together –
Valentine-themed paw painting in pairs.
🐾 Heart-Shaped Relay –
A romantic quest to collect the most hearts.

Will it be love at first sniff? Sign up for 'Love Unleashed' to join in our activities and fill your life with puppy love 💖 

#OnCloudCanine #DoggyDaycare #PetSitting #AkronOH #DogTraining #DogGrooming #FearFree #DogEnrichment #EnrichmentDaycare #EnrichmentForDogs #LoveUnleashed

🌟 Employee Spotlight 🌟 A pawsome addition to our pack: Jenna! 

Jenna has been dedicated to animals since she was young, helping care for foster pets and standing strong against animal testing. In 2017, she became an assistant groomer and quickly realized her true calling!

When she’s not pampering pups, Jenna loves attending concerts, kayaking, traveling, and learning new things. At home, she’s got her hands full with her three beloved cats, Newton, Miso, and Goose, and her precious pup, Finley! 🐱🐱🐱🐶

We’re so lucky to have her as part of our team! Let's give Jenna a big round of applause for all the dedication and expertise she brings to On Cloud Canine 👏👏

#OnCloudCanine #EmployeeSpotlight #FearFree #AkronOH #DogGrooming #CatGrooming #MeetThePack #DoggyDaycare #DogTraining #PetSitting

We are happy to report that your pups have been LOVING the new Scent Den! 💖 🐾

This enrichment experience offers a natural way to reduce anxiety, boost stimulation, and promote relaxation 😌 Whether it's during daycare or a groom, it will be an adventure they won't forget! 

We all deserve to stop and smell the roses 🌹 Sign up today!

💌 February Enrichment Week 3: Love is right around the corner! 💌

This week is all about interaction and chemistry 💘 We'll observe which pups bond and who's got that special connection, but the final pairing is still a mystery! Here's what's on the menu this week: 

🐾 Valentine Chews – Paired-Up Dinner Time with a Long-Lasting Treat
🐾 Romantic Candlelit Dinner – A Sweet Setting and Our Finest Bottle (Chicken Broth)
🐾 Who’s Your Match? – Sniff Out the Best Smell and a Potential Partner
🐾Nature Walk Duos – A Stroll in Nature to See Who Has a Matching Stride
🐾 Tug of Heartstrings – Pull a Partner in with a Competitive Game of Tug

Join us for 'Love Unleashed' to partake in these pawsome activities! 
Learn, explore, play - sign up today 💖

Don’t miss the latest episode of Love Unleashed on YouTube! ❤️ 

We’d love for you to join us on Love Unleashed! In this week’s episode, Bella has plenty of options—but will she make the right choice? Solo, the pup who’s more into chew toys than romance, steals the spotlight, while Dolly Parton steps up to show she’s the true leader of the pack. Will love bloom, or will it all go to the dogs?

💌 February Enrichment Week 2: Love is in the Air! 💌

Cupid’s been busy at On Cloud Canine, and this week’s enrichment menu is all about showing off your pup’s skills 🐶💘 Here’s the pawsome lineup for this week:

🐾 Cupid’s Cookie Hunt – Sniff out Cupid’s hidden cookies 🍪
🐾 Sweetheart’s Scent Trail – Follow the love ‘note’ that speaks to the heart 💌
🐾 The Cupid Code – Solve the puzzle to unlock a love letter 🔎
🐾 Trick Training in Pairs – Synchronized tricks to show off chemistry ✨
🐾 Leap for Love – Leap through hoops to find the best match 🐕

Join us for 'Love Unleashed' to show your pet what puppy love is all about!
Learn, explore, play - sign up today 💖

Gerry and Gracie are swiping right on the ‘Love Unleashed’ doggy dating show! In this lighthearted event, dogs will have the chance to “meet” other pups in a variety of fun and engaging activities, all while you enjoy the love connections from the sidelines. From playtime to a “doggy speed dating” round, we’ll help your pup find their pawfect match. Whether you’re looking to spark a new friendship for your dog or just want to join in on the fun, Love Unleashed is the paw-some event you won’t want to miss! 🚨 Our Pet of the Month Contest is Back! 

Think your pet has what it takes to be our next star? 🌟 Enter now for a chance to win a special goodie bag AND a free service! 

Here’s how to enter:
1️⃣ Like this post 
2️⃣ Tag a friend in the comments 🐕
